        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 3 at 12:52AM CDT until August 3 at 1:15AM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 1252 AM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 9 miles southeast
of Adrian, or 11 miles southwest of Vega, moving southeast at 30 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Vega, Adrian, and Simms.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
